{"tid":1700343,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"楊衞隆：茶黨正勸麥康奈爾於11月12日提出人權法表決，唔好接受林鄭任何offer.","createTime":"2019-11-08T13:03:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T14:27:29.000Z","uid":189404,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"28d63bb8b89b14170e2e9e52cef1a03ea4292459","tid":1700343,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:03:18.000Z","msg":"廣傳：楊衞隆：<br />\n#茶黨正在勸導參議院多數派領袖麥康奈爾於11月12日星期二提出香港人權及民主法表決。老麥是2011年茶黨黨團4位成員之一又是茶黨掌控參議院的功臣。他現在於參議院及茶黨仍有一定影響力。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#林賤可能會在11月11日之前宣佈獨立調查黑警暴行。林賤是個厚顏無恥之人，換可憐，裝仁慈，口是心非的奸險小人。#無論她怎樣說，#只是緩兵之計，#千萬不要接受。<br />\n<br />\n楊衛隆雖然神化d,但係茶黨老人，可以參考下。"},{"pid":"ed3d9912b9c33791bf81268c0adf4e7dbfff1b8b","tid":1700343,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:04:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dce8c8b807e0a7955347dcac395e68220eb4d8c","tid":1700343,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:05:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f7c23b6b5812d05fe16f5aa4f2f3ea11fdfbda8","tid":1700343,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【行動】請大中小學學生整理身邊失聯同學名冊，用作紀錄反送中死難學生名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1700288</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"efe9fc5d6a67fbe55a65b50e234fa463ce0f31ed","tid":1700343,"uid":189404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f7c23b6b5812d05fe16f5aa4f2f3ea11fdfbda8","tid":1700343,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T13:05:29.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【行動】請大中小學學生整理身邊失聯同學名冊，用作紀錄反送中死難學生名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1700288\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\"